011cooperation, whereas Candidate\u202fB\u2019s core safety\u2011critical attributes are clearly present and outweigh the interpersonal shortcomings, which are less severe than the red flags in the other candidates.\n**Conclusion:** Candidate\u202fB is the most suitable choice for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
